{
  "video_id": "coHWLitlm-U",
  "title": "Activism needs introverts | Sarah Corbett",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12667.0,
      "end_time": 14762.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, about seven years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14786.0,
      "end_time": 18535.0,
      "text": "I found myself hiding in a festival toilet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18559.0,
      "end_time": 20358.0,
      "text": "a music festival toilet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20382.0,
      "end_time": 23509.0,
      "text": "and if anyone&#39;s been to a music festival,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23533.0,
      "end_time": 27454.0,
      "text": "yeah, you&#39;ll know that by the third day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27478.0,
      "end_time": 29167.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s pretty nasty."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29191.0,
      "end_time": 32476.0,
      "text": "I was standing in the toilet because I couldn&#39;t even sit down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32500.0,
      "end_time": 35184.0,
      "text": "because the toilet roll had run out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35208.0,
      "end_time": 36652.0,
      "text": "there was mud everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36676.0,
      "end_time": 38101.0,
      "text": "and it smelled pretty bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38125.0,
      "end_time": 39902.0,
      "text": "And I stood there thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39926.0,
      "end_time": 42934.0,
      "text": "\"What am I doing? I don&#39;t even need the toilet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42958.0,
      "end_time": 44315.0,
      "text": "But the reason I went"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44340.0,
      "end_time": 48776.0,
      "text": "was because I was volunteering for a large charity on climate justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48800.0,
      "end_time": 50708.0,
      "text": "and it was seven years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50732.0,
      "end_time": 53223.0,
      "text": "when lots of people didn&#39;t believe in climate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53247.0,
      "end_time": 55152.0,
      "text": "people were very cynical about activism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55176.0,
      "end_time": 57340.0,
      "text": "and my role, with all of my teammates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57580.0,
      "end_time": 60590.0,
      "text": "was to get people to sign petitions on climate justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60830.0,
      "end_time": 62637.0,
      "text": "and educate them a bit more about the issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62661.0,
      "end_time": 66558.0,
      "text": "And I cared deeply about climate change and lots of inequality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66582.0,
      "end_time": 68535.0,
      "text": "so I&#39;d go and I&#39;d talk to lots of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68559.0,
      "end_time": 71789.0,
      "text": "which made me nervous and drained me of energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71813.0,
      "end_time": 73638.0,
      "text": "but I did it because I cared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73662.0,
      "end_time": 77567.0,
      "text": "but I would hide in the toilets, because I&#39;d be exhausted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77591.0,
      "end_time": 81535.0,
      "text": "and I didn&#39;t want my teammates doubting my commitment to the cause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81560.0,
      "end_time": 83441.0,
      "text": "thinking that I was slacking."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83465.0,
      "end_time": 85608.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;d go and meet at the end of our shift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85632.0,
      "end_time": 87997.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;d count how many petitions had been signed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88210.0,
      "end_time": 90688.0,
      "text": "and often I&#39;d win the amount of petitions signed"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90712.0,
      "end_time": 93251.0,
      "text": "even though I had my little breaks in the toilet."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93275.0,
      "end_time": 96220.0,
      "text": "But I was always very jealous of the other activists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96460.0,
      "end_time": 98410.0,
      "text": "because either they had the same amount of energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98434.0,
      "end_time": 103109.0,
      "text": "as they had when they began the shift of getting people to sign petitions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103133.0,
      "end_time": 105770.0,
      "text": "or often they had more energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105101.0,
      "end_time": 108602.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;d be really excited about going to watch the bands in the evening"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108626.0,
      "end_time": 109800.0,
      "text": "and having a dance."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109824.0,
      "end_time": 111935.0,
      "text": "And even if I loved the bands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111959.0,
      "end_time": 115940.0,
      "text": "all I wanted to do was to go back to my tent and have a sleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115118.0,
      "end_time": 117785.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;d just feel completely wiped out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117809.0,
      "end_time": 120366.0,
      "text": "and I was really jealous of people that had the energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 120390.0,
      "end_time": 122920.0,
      "text": "to go and party hard at the festivals."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123703.0,
      "end_time": 126615.0,
      "text": "But it also made me really angry, as well, inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126639.0,
      "end_time": 129561.0,
      "text": "I thought, \"This isn&#39;t fair, I&#39;m an introvert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 129585.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134505.0,
      "text": "and all of the offline campaigning seems to be favoring extroverts.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135340.0,
      "end_time": 137232.0,
      "text": "I would go on marches which drained me."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137256.0,
      "end_time": 138518.0,
      "text": "That was the other option."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138542.0,
      "end_time": 142943.0,
      "text": "Or I&#39;d go and join campaigns outside embassies or shops."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142967.0,
      "end_time": 145912.0,
      "text": "The only thing that was on offer was around lots of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 145936.0,
      "end_time": 147888.0,
      "text": "it was very loud activism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 147912.0,
      "end_time": 150935.0,
      "text": "it always involved lots of people, it was performing."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150959.0,
      "end_time": 153190.0,
      "text": "None of it was for introverts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 153214.0,
      "end_time": 155857.0,
      "text": "and I not only thought that that wasn&#39;t fair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 155881.0,
      "end_time": 160707.0,
      "text": "because a third to a half of the world&#39;s population are introverts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 160731.0,
      "end_time": 163745.0,
      "text": "which isn&#39;t fair on them, because we burn out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 163770.0,
      "end_time": 166327.0,
      "text": "or we&#39;d be put off by activism and not do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166351.0,
      "end_time": 170106.0,
      "text": "and everyone needs to be an activist in this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170414.0,
      "end_time": 173550.0,
      "text": "And also, I didn&#39;t think it was particularly clever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173800.0,
      "end_time": 176811.0,
      "text": "but I could see that a lot of the activism that worked"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176835.0,
      "end_time": 179820.0,
      "text": "wasn&#39;t only extrovert activism."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 179106.0,
      "end_time": 180851.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t only the loud stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 180875.0,
      "end_time": 183764.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t about people performing all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183788.0,
      "end_time": 186409.0,
      "text": "A lot of the work that was needed was in the background,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186433.0,
      "end_time": 188375.0,
      "text": "was hidden, wasn&#39;t seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 189310.0,
      "end_time": 191419.0,
      "text": "And when I ended up just being a campaigner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 191443.0,
      "end_time": 193562.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s the only job I can do, really --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 193586.0,
      "end_time": 195301.0,
      "text": "I was campaigning at university,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 195325.0,
      "end_time": 198357.0,
      "text": "and for the last 10 years, I&#39;ve been a professional campaigner"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198381.0,
      "end_time": 199548.0,
      "text": "for large charities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 199572.0,
      "end_time": 203421.0,
      "text": "and now I&#39;m a creative campaigner consultant for different charities"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 203445.0,
      "end_time": 205709.0,
      "text": "as well as other work I do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 205733.0,
      "end_time": 208945.0,
      "text": "but I knew that there were other forms of activism that were needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 209607.0,
      "end_time": 212163.0,
      "text": "I started tinkering about seven years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 212187.0,
      "end_time": 215941.0,
      "text": "to see what quieter forms of activism I could engage with"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 215965.0,
      "end_time": 218242.0,
      "text": "so I didn&#39;t burn out as an activist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 218266.0,
      "end_time": 223280.0,
      "text": "but also to look at some of the issues I was concerned about in campaigning."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 223520.0,
      "end_time": 226482.0,
      "text": "I was very lucky that, when I worked for Oxfam and other big charities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226506.0,
      "end_time": 228704.0,
      "text": "I could read lots of big reports"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 228728.0,
      "end_time": 231982.0,
      "text": "on what influenced politicians and businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 232600.0,
      "end_time": 233697.0,
      "text": "and the general public,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 233721.0,
      "end_time": 236199.0,
      "text": "what campaigns worked really well, which ones didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 236223.0,
      "end_time": 239158.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m a bit of a geek, so I look at all of that stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 239182.0,
      "end_time": 240564.0,
      "text": "and I wanted to tinker around"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 240588.0,
      "end_time": 244453.0,
      "text": "to see how I could engage people in social change in a different way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 244477.0,
      "end_time": 249720.0,
      "text": "because I think if we want the world to be more beautiful, kind and just,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 249960.0,
      "end_time": 252889.0,
      "text": "then our activism should be beautiful, kind and just,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 252913.0,
      "end_time": 254278.0,
      "text": "and often it&#39;s not."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 254723.0,
      "end_time": 257630.0,
      "text": "And today, I just want to talk about three ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 257870.0,
      "end_time": 259158.0,
      "text": "that I think activism needs introverts."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 259596.0,
      "end_time": 263800.0,
      "text": "I think there&#39;s lot of other ways, but I&#39;m just going to talk about three."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 263731.0,
      "end_time": 267747.0,
      "text": "And the first one is: activism is often very quick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 267771.0,
      "end_time": 269810.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s about doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 269105.0,
      "end_time": 272360.0,
      "text": "so extroverts, often their immediate response to injustice is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 272384.0,
      "end_time": 273844.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve got to do stuff now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 273868.0,
      "end_time": 275678.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve got to react really quickly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 275702.0,
      "end_time": 277317.0,
      "text": "and yes, we do need to react,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 277341.0,
      "end_time": 279937.0,
      "text": "but we need to be strategic in our campaigning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 279961.0,
      "end_time": 281587.0,
      "text": "and if we just act on anger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 281611.0,
      "end_time": 283284.0,
      "text": "often we do the wrong things."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 284177.0,
      "end_time": 286805.0,
      "text": "I use craft, like needlework --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 286829.0,
      "end_time": 288908.0,
      "text": "like this guy behind me is doing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 288932.0,
      "end_time": 292766.0,
      "text": "as a way to not only slow down those extrovert doers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 292790.0,
      "end_time": 298548.0,
      "text": "but also to bring in nervous, quiet introverts into activism."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 299216.0,
      "end_time": 301727.0,
      "text": "By doing repetitive actions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 301751.0,
      "end_time": 304765.0,
      "text": "like handicraft, you can&#39;t do it fast, you have to do it slowly."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 304789.0,
      "end_time": 306500.0,
      "text": "And those repetitive stitches"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 306524.0,
      "end_time": 310588.0,
      "text": "help you meditate on the big, complex, messy social change issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 310612.0,
      "end_time": 312960.0,
      "text": "and figure out what we can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 312984.0,
      "end_time": 318388.0,
      "text": "as a citizen, as a consumer, as a constituent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 318413.0,
      "end_time": 320397.0,
      "text": "and all of those different things."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 320421.0,
      "end_time": 323818.0,
      "text": "It helps you think critically while you&#39;re stitching away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 323842.0,
      "end_time": 326558.0,
      "text": "and it helps you be more mindful of what are your motives."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 326582.0,
      "end_time": 329930.0,
      "text": "Are you that Barbie aid worker that was mentioned before?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 329954.0,
      "end_time": 332605.0,
      "text": "Are you about joining people in solidarity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 332629.0,
      "end_time": 335805.0,
      "text": "or do you want to be the savior, which often isn&#39;t very ethical?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 335829.0,
      "end_time": 338177.0,
      "text": "But doing needle work together, as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 338201.0,
      "end_time": 341868.0,
      "text": "extroverts and introverts and ambivert --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 341892.0,
      "end_time": 344115.0,
      "text": "everyone&#39;s on the scale in different places --"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 344139.0,
      "end_time": 348893.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s a quiet, slow form of activism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 348917.0,
      "end_time": 351686.0,
      "text": "it really helps introverts be heard"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 351711.0,
      "end_time": 355579.0,
      "text": "in other areas, where they are often not heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 355603.0,
      "end_time": 358253.0,
      "text": "It sounds odd,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 358277.0,
      "end_time": 361905.0,
      "text": "but while you&#39;re stitching, you don&#39;t need eye contact with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 361929.0,
      "end_time": 364410.0,
      "text": "So, for nervous introverts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 364650.0,
      "end_time": 368255.0,
      "text": "it means that you can stitch away next to someone or a group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 368279.0,
      "end_time": 370478.0,
      "text": "and ask questions that you&#39;re thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 370502.0,
      "end_time": 373565.0,
      "text": "that often you don&#39;t get time to ask people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 373589.0,
      "end_time": 376486.0,
      "text": "or you&#39;re too nervous to ask if you give them eye contact."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 376510.0,
      "end_time": 379462.0,
      "text": "So you can get introverts, who are those big, deep thinkers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 379486.0,
      "end_time": 382652.0,
      "text": "saying, \"That&#39;s really interesting that you want to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 382677.0,
      "end_time": 385893.0,
      "text": "that extrovert form of activism that&#39;s about shaming people"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 385917.0,
      "end_time": 387607.0,
      "text": "or quickly going out somewhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 387632.0,
      "end_time": 389806.0,
      "text": "but who are you trying to target and how,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 389830.0,
      "end_time": 391758.0,
      "text": "and is that the best way to do it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 391783.0,
      "end_time": 394830.0,
      "text": "So it means you could have these discussions in a very slow way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 394854.0,
      "end_time": 397830.0,
      "text": "which is great for the extrovert to slow down and think deeply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 397855.0,
      "end_time": 400620.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s really good for the introvert as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 400860.0,
      "end_time": 403641.0,
      "text": "to be heard and to feel part of that movement for change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 403665.0,
      "end_time": 404816.0,
      "text": "in a good way."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 404840.0,
      "end_time": 407222.0,
      "text": "Some ways we do it is stitch cards"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 407246.0,
      "end_time": 410308.0,
      "text": "about what values we thread through our activism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 410333.0,
      "end_time": 413841.0,
      "text": "and making sure that we don&#39;t just react in unethical ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 413865.0,
      "end_time": 416675.0,
      "text": "One, sometimes we work with art institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 416699.0,
      "end_time": 419771.0,
      "text": "where we will get over 150 people at the V&A"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 419795.0,
      "end_time": 421245.0,
      "text": "who can come for hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 421269.0,
      "end_time": 423706.0,
      "text": "sit and stitch together on a particular issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 423730.0,
      "end_time": 427191.0,
      "text": "and then tweet what they&#39;re thinking or how it went, like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 427727.0,
      "end_time": 430950.0,
      "text": "Also, I always think that activism needs introverts"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 430974.0,
      "end_time": 433989.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re really good at intimate activism."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 434130.0,
      "end_time": 435640.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re good at slow activism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 435664.0,
      "end_time": 437950.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re really good at intimate activism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 437974.0,
      "end_time": 439816.0,
      "text": "and if this year has told us anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 439840.0,
      "end_time": 443681.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s told us that we need to, when we&#39;re engaging power holders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 443705.0,
      "end_time": 447150.0,
      "text": "we need to engage them by listening to people we disagree with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 447390.0,
      "end_time": 449145.0,
      "text": "by building bridges not walls --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 449169.0,
      "end_time": 451950.0,
      "text": "walls or wars --"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 451975.0,
      "end_time": 454879.0,
      "text": "and by being critical friends, not aggressive enemies."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 455371.0,
      "end_time": 458245.0,
      "text": "And one example that I do a lot with introverts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 458269.0,
      "end_time": 459420.0,
      "text": "but with lots of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 459444.0,
      "end_time": 461530.0,
      "text": "is make gifts for people in power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 461554.0,
      "end_time": 464157.0,
      "text": "so not be outside screaming at them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 464182.0,
      "end_time": 467860.0,
      "text": "but to give them something like a bespoke handkerchief"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 467110.0,
      "end_time": 468445.0,
      "text": "saying, \"Don&#39;t blow it."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 468469.0,
      "end_time": 469976.0,
      "text": "Use your power for good."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 470000.0,
      "end_time": 473151.0,
      "text": "We know you&#39;ve got a difficult job in your position of power."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 473175.0,
      "end_time": 474913.0,
      "text": "How can we help you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 474937.0,
      "end_time": 477652.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s great is, for the introverts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 477676.0,
      "end_time": 480111.0,
      "text": "we can write letters while we&#39;re making these gifts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 480136.0,
      "end_time": 482509.0,
      "text": "so for us, Marks and Spencer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 482533.0,
      "end_time": 486954.0,
      "text": "we tried to campaign to get them to implement the living wage."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 486978.0,
      "end_time": 491200.0,
      "text": "So we made all the 14 board members bespoke handkerchiefs."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 491440.0,
      "end_time": 493335.0,
      "text": "We wrote them letters, we boxed them up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 493360.0,
      "end_time": 496393.0,
      "text": "and we went to the AGM to hand-deliver our gifts"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 496417.0,
      "end_time": 498912.0,
      "text": "and to have that form of intimate activism"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 498937.0,
      "end_time": 500678.0,
      "text": "where we had discussions with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 501107.0,
      "end_time": 504290.0,
      "text": "And what was brilliant was that the chair of the board"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 504314.0,
      "end_time": 506266.0,
      "text": "told us how amazing our campaign was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 506290.0,
      "end_time": 507726.0,
      "text": "how heartfelt it was."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 508153.0,
      "end_time": 510257.0,
      "text": "The board members, like Martha Lane Fox,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 510281.0,
      "end_time": 513185.0,
      "text": "who has hundreds of thousands of followers on Twitter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 513207.99999999994,
      "end_time": 515485.99999999994,
      "text": "and highly influential in business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 515510.0,
      "end_time": 517534.0,
      "text": "tweeted how impressed she was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 517558.0,
      "end_time": 519145.0,
      "text": "and within 10 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 519169.0,
      "end_time": 521726.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d had meetings with Marks and Spencer"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 521750.0,
      "end_time": 525290.0,
      "text": "to say, \"We know this is difficult to be a living wage employer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 525314.0,
      "end_time": 526663.0,
      "text": "but if you can be one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 526687.0,
      "end_time": 528546.0,
      "text": "the rest of the sector will look at it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 528570.0,
      "end_time": 533172.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s not right that some of your amazing workers are working full time"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 533196.0,
      "end_time": 534735.0,
      "text": "and still can&#39;t pay their bills."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 534759.0,
      "end_time": 536259.0,
      "text": "And we love Marks and Spencer."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 536283.0,
      "end_time": 538989.0,
      "text": "How can you be the role model that we want you to be?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 539829.0,
      "end_time": 541838.0,
      "text": "So that was that intimate form of activism."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 541862.0,
      "end_time": 544163.0,
      "text": "We had lots of meetings with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 544187.0,
      "end_time": 548686.0,
      "text": "We then gave them Christmas cards and Valentine&#39;s cards to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 548710.0,
      "end_time": 552130.0,
      "text": "\"We really want to encourage you to implement the living wage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 552370.0,
      "end_time": 554845.0,
      "text": "and within 10 months, they&#39;d announced to the media"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 554869.0,
      "end_time": 558735.0,
      "text": "that they were going to pay the independent living wage, and now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 558759.0,
      "end_time": 560568.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 560592.0,
      "end_time": 561742.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 561767.0,
      "end_time": 565306.0,
      "text": "And now we&#39;re trying to work with them to be accredited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 565330.0,
      "end_time": 566609.0,
      "text": "which is really important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 566633.0,
      "end_time": 569850.0,
      "text": "and we went back to the last AGM this June"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 569109.0,
      "end_time": 572705.0,
      "text": "and we had these amazing one-to-one discussions with the board members,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 572729.0,
      "end_time": 574826.0,
      "text": "who told us how much they loved their hankies"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 574850.0,
      "end_time": 577724.0,
      "text": "and how it really moved them, what we were doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 577748.0,
      "end_time": 581212.0,
      "text": "and they all told us that if we were standing outside screaming at them"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 581236.0,
      "end_time": 583356.0,
      "text": "and not being gentle in our protest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 583380.0,
      "end_time": 585257.0,
      "text": "they wouldn&#39;t have even listened to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 585281.0,
      "end_time": 587308.0,
      "text": "never mind had those discussions with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 587332.0,
      "end_time": 590689.0,
      "text": "And I think introverts are really good at intimate activism"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 590714.0,
      "end_time": 592550.0,
      "text": "because we like to listen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 592790.0,
      "end_time": 593435.0,
      "text": "we like one-to-ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 593460.0,
      "end_time": 594807.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t like small talks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 594831.0,
      "end_time": 598357.0,
      "text": "we like those big, juicy issues to discuss with people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 598381.0,
      "end_time": 599896.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t like conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 599921.0,
      "end_time": 601688.0,
      "text": "so we avoid it at all costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 601712.0,
      "end_time": 605100.0,
      "text": "which is really important when we&#39;re trying to engage power holders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 605250.0,
      "end_time": 608194.0,
      "text": "not to be conflicting with them all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 608632.0,
      "end_time": 613325.0,
      "text": "The third way I think activists are really missing out"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 613350.0,
      "end_time": 615220.0,
      "text": "if they don&#39;t engage introverts"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 615244.0,
      "end_time": 620275.0,
      "text": "is that introverts, like I said, can be half of the world&#39;s population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 620299.0,
      "end_time": 623403.0,
      "text": "and most of us won&#39;t say that we&#39;re introvert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 623427.0,
      "end_time": 626621.0,
      "text": "or we get embarrassed by saying what overwhelms us."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 626645.0,
      "end_time": 628646.0,
      "text": "So for me, a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 628670.0,
      "end_time": 631762.0,
      "text": "my mom used to send me texts in capital letters --"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 631787.0,
      "end_time": 634937.0,
      "text": "and she can now do emojis and everything, she&#39;s fine --"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 634961.0,
      "end_time": 636740.0,
      "text": "but as soon as I&#39;d see this text,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 636764.0,
      "end_time": 640384.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d wince and think, \"Ooh, it&#39;s capital letters, it&#39;s too much.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 640408.0,
      "end_time": 643590.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d have to ignore it to read the lovely text she sent me."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 643614.0,
      "end_time": 645970.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s a bit embarrassing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 645121.0,
      "end_time": 648233.0,
      "text": "to tell people that capital letters overwhelm you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 648257.0,
      "end_time": 653266.0,
      "text": "but we really need introverts to help us do intriguing activism"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 653290.0,
      "end_time": 655853.0,
      "text": "that attracts them rather than puts them off."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 655877.0,
      "end_time": 659329.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re put off by big and brash giant posters"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 659354.0,
      "end_time": 661862.0,
      "text": "and capital letters and explanation marks"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 661886.0,
      "end_time": 665308.0,
      "text": "telling us what to do and vying for our attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 665332.0,
      "end_time": 669130.0,
      "text": "So some of the things I do with people around the world who take part"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 669154.0,
      "end_time": 671496.0,
      "text": "is make small bits of provocative street art"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 671520.0,
      "end_time": 674162.0,
      "text": "which are hung off eye level, very small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 674186.0,
      "end_time": 675964.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re provocative messages."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 675988.0,
      "end_time": 679273.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not preaching at people or telling them what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 679297.0,
      "end_time": 681931.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re just getting people to engage in different ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 681955.0,
      "end_time": 683146.0,
      "text": "and think for themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 683170.0,
      "end_time": 685295.0,
      "text": "because we don&#39;t like to be told what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 685921.0,
      "end_time": 688374.0,
      "text": "It might be wearing a green heart on your sleeve"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 688398.0,
      "end_time": 691295.0,
      "text": "saying what you love and how climate change will affect it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 691319.0,
      "end_time": 692477.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll wear it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 692501.0,
      "end_time": 693683.0,
      "text": "and if people say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 693707.0,
      "end_time": 697400.0,
      "text": "\"Why are you wearing a green heart with the word &#39;chocolate&#39; on?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 697650.0,
      "end_time": 700231.0,
      "text": "and we can have those one-to-one intimate conversations and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 700255.0,
      "end_time": 701446.0,
      "text": "\"I love chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 701470.0,
      "end_time": 703712.0,
      "text": "Climate change is going to affect it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 703736.0,
      "end_time": 707183.0,
      "text": "and I think there&#39;s lot of other things that climate change will affect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 707207.0,
      "end_time": 710750.0,
      "text": "and I really want to make sure I&#39;m part of the solution, not the problem.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 710774.0,
      "end_time": 714353.0,
      "text": "And then we deflect, because we don&#39;t like to be the center of attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 714377.0,
      "end_time": 717503.0,
      "text": "and say, \"What do you love and how will climate change affect it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 718710.0,
      "end_time": 720834.0,
      "text": "Or it might be shop-dropping instead of shop-lifting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 720858.0,
      "end_time": 724714.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;ll make little mini-scrolls with lovely stories on"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 724739.0,
      "end_time": 727970.0,
      "text": "about what&#39;s the story behind your clothes."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 727121.0,
      "end_time": 731970.0,
      "text": "Is it a joyful story of how it&#39;s made, or is it a torturous one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 731121.0,
      "end_time": 733918.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ll just drop them in little pockets in shops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 733942.0,
      "end_time": 736177.0,
      "text": "all lowercase, all handwritten,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 736201.0,
      "end_time": 739551.0,
      "text": "with kisses and smiley faces in ribbon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 739575.0,
      "end_time": 742173.0,
      "text": "and then people are excited that they found it."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 742197.0,
      "end_time": 744559.0,
      "text": "And we often drop them in unethical shops"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 744583.0,
      "end_time": 746677.0,
      "text": "or in front pockets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 746701.0,
      "end_time": 749946.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a way that we can do offline campaigning"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 749970.0,
      "end_time": 752431.0,
      "text": "that engages us and doesn&#39;t burn us out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 752455.0,
      "end_time": 757711.0,
      "text": "but also engages other people in an intriguing way online and offline."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 759610.0,
      "end_time": 762209.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve got two calls to action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 762233.0,
      "end_time": 765218.0,
      "text": "for the introverts and for the extroverts."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 765242.0,
      "end_time": 766741.0,
      "text": "For the ambivert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 766765.0,
      "end_time": 768146.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re involved in all of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 769550.0,
      "end_time": 774100.0,
      "text": "For the extroverts, I want to say that when you&#39;re planning a campaign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 774250.0,
      "end_time": 775540.0,
      "text": "think about introverts."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 775565.0,
      "end_time": 779461.0,
      "text": "Think about how valuable our skills are, just as much as extroverts&#39;."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 780170.0,
      "end_time": 782776.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re good at slowing down and thinking deeply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 782800.0,
      "end_time": 785992.0,
      "text": "and the detail of issues, we&#39;re really good at bringing them out."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 786673.0,
      "end_time": 790728.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re good at intimate activism, so use us in that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 790752.0,
      "end_time": 793450.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re good at intriguing people"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 793690.0,
      "end_time": 797779.0,
      "text": "by doing strange little things that help create conversations and thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 797803.0,
      "end_time": 800999.0,
      "text": "Introverts, my call to action for you is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 801230.0,
      "end_time": 802801.0,
      "text": "I know you like being on your own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 802825.0,
      "end_time": 804676.0,
      "text": "I know you like being in your head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 804700.0,
      "end_time": 806597.0,
      "text": "but activism needs you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 806621.0,
      "end_time": 808653.0,
      "text": "so sometimes you&#39;ve got to get out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 808677.0,
      "end_time": 812110.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t mean that you&#39;ve got to turn into an extrovert and burn out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 812350.0,
      "end_time": 813607.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s no use for anyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 813631.0,
      "end_time": 814828.0,
      "text": "but what it does mean"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 814852.0,
      "end_time": 818795.0,
      "text": "is that you should value the skills and the traits that you have"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 818820.0,
      "end_time": 820272.0,
      "text": "that activism needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 820835.0,
      "end_time": 822399.0,
      "text": "So for everyone in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 822423.0,
      "end_time": 826232.0,
      "text": "whether you&#39;re an extrovert or an introvert or an ambivert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 826256.0,
      "end_time": 829137.0,
      "text": "the world needs you now more than ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 829161.0,
      "end_time": 831493.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;ve got no excuse not to get involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 831922.0,
      "end_time": 833730.0,
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 833970.0,
      "end_time": 836309.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}